WEBVTT

00:00.007 --> 00:01.789
Previously on "When Calls the Heart"...

00:01.814 --> 00:04.041
I know it's not the best parcel
in Hope Valley...

00:04.070 --> 00:05.569
But it's all yours.

00:05.604 --> 00:07.805
And I've seen the way you
two look at each other.

00:07.881 --> 00:10.037
Thank you for keeping our secret.

00:11.008 --> 00:12.475
You said they were two
of the worst gunrunners

00:12.500 --> 00:13.547
we've ever seen.

00:13.572 --> 00:15.347
You'll go to jail for this!

00:18.442 --> 00:19.578
Hello.

00:19.603 --> 00:22.350
Welcome to Hope Valley, Constable.

00:29.213 --> 00:30.684
You should take a break.

00:31.653 --> 00:33.047
Ah, I'm fine. Thank you.

00:33.072 --> 00:34.471
You're welcome.

00:35.303 --> 00:36.636
[SIGHS]

00:36.661 --> 00:38.164
[REFRESHED SIGH]

00:38.995 --> 00:40.405
You know, I have to admit,

00:40.430 --> 00:42.425
digging a well is a lot
harder than I thought.

00:42.450 --> 00:44.164
[LAUGHS]

00:49.641 --> 00:56.836
<i>[REPETITIVE CLINKING OF CHINA]</i>

01:04.376 --> 01:06.513
<i>You gotta be kidding me?</i>

01:07.190 --> 01:08.860
<i>Oh...</i>

01:09.692 --> 01:11.025
<i>Bill!</i>

01:12.045 --> 01:14.846
<i>[LOUD RUMBLING SOUND]</i>

01:14.871 --> 01:17.704
<i>[DISHES CLATTERING, FLOOR SHAKING]</i>

01:18.659 --> 01:20.491
[SIGHS]

01:20.748 --> 01:22.663
Tremors always scare me.

01:22.885 --> 01:25.120
Nothing good ever comes of 'em.

01:28.089 --> 01:29.169
Did you feel that?

01:29.194 --> 01:30.893
Yeah. That was weird.

01:31.820 --> 01:33.252
<i>[BUBBLING SOUND]</i>

01:33.277 --> 01:35.565
Did you hit water already?

01:37.457 --> 01:39.044
Woah!

01:43.309 --> 01:44.641
What is it?

01:49.426 --> 01:50.779
Is it?

01:53.262 --> 01:54.998
[LAUGHS IN DISBELIEF]

01:55.182 --> 01:56.299
It's oil!

01:56.324 --> 01:57.802
[LAUGHS]

01:57.827 --> 01:59.295
Oh my goodness!

01:59.717 --> 02:01.101
We're gonna be rich!

02:01.126 --> 02:03.171
[BOTH LAUGHING]

02:03.465 --> 02:05.024
Wooo!

02:06.629 --> 02:21.542
♪

02:21.578 --> 02:32.779
♪

02:32.804 --> 02:37.009
- Synced and corrected by martythecrazy -
- www.addic7ed.com -

02:40.053 --> 02:41.119
See?

02:41.144 --> 02:42.507
What did I tell ya?

02:42.532 --> 02:43.964
You weren't kiddin'.

02:44.000 --> 02:45.493
So, what do I do now?

02:45.722 --> 02:47.986
First off, you might
wanna talk to an expert.

02:48.011 --> 02:49.991
What, so he can tell me
what I can already see?

02:50.016 --> 02:51.949
So he can tell you
what's happening here.

02:51.974 --> 02:54.875
'Cause people don't just
strike oil four feet down.

02:54.900 --> 02:55.782
How do you know?

02:55.807 --> 02:58.758
He's, he's right, Jessie,
this is not normal.

02:59.846 --> 03:02.376
I know a geologist
over in Benson Hills,

03:02.401 --> 03:04.930
maybe if I talk to him, he'll
come out and have a look.

03:05.104 --> 03:07.064
You can use my telephone if you want.

03:07.089 --> 03:08.984
All right, let's do it.

03:13.307 --> 03:14.760
Thank you.

03:17.323 --> 03:18.843
[SURPRISED] Oh!

03:18.868 --> 03:20.280
Is everyone fine?

03:20.305 --> 03:21.906
Yes, baby Jack didn't even wake up.

03:21.941 --> 03:22.886
Oh, good.

03:22.911 --> 03:25.662
We want momma rocking the
baby, not Mother Nature.

03:25.839 --> 03:27.091
Very true.

03:27.116 --> 03:28.816
Anyway, thanks so much for
checking on us, Rosemary,

03:28.841 --> 03:30.272
but I've really got to get to school.

03:30.322 --> 03:31.658
Elizabeth...

03:36.019 --> 03:39.713
I feel our friendship may
be dying on the vine.

03:40.236 --> 03:41.468
Excuse me?

03:41.493 --> 03:43.542
We never see each other anymore.

03:43.567 --> 03:45.834
Rosemary, we're neighbours,
I see you every day.

03:45.859 --> 03:48.460
A wave from the window does
not a friendship make.

03:48.485 --> 03:50.222
Next it'll be little nods,
and before you know it,

03:50.247 --> 03:53.082
we'll be avoiding eye
contact altogether.

03:53.550 --> 03:56.817
I'm sorry. I have had to cancel
dinner plans a couple of times.

03:56.842 --> 03:58.475
If by a couple, you mean five.

03:58.500 --> 03:59.548
Then, yes.

03:59.573 --> 04:01.545
Rosemary, your friendship
means the world to me.

04:01.570 --> 04:02.489
Good.

04:02.514 --> 04:04.038
Then, you'll join us
for dinner tonight.

04:04.063 --> 04:04.782
Tonight?

04:04.807 --> 04:05.941
Mm-hmm.

04:06.484 --> 04:08.611
Absolutely. Sounds great.

04:09.190 --> 04:10.153
Wonderful!

04:10.178 --> 04:11.528
I'll see you then.

